## Quality Rules (HQVF)

1. **NEVER develop without approved UCV** - UCVs are the contract
2. **Every story needs STORY-XXX-UCV.md** - No exceptions
3. **Mark verifications as completed** - Track progress
4. **Story DONE = 100% UCVs validated** - Objective completion

